Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(335,280)\fs20}九州地区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(545,280)\fs20}福冈基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在此宣告  再兴正统的独立主权国家日本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,占据了福冈基地的组织中心人物   泽崎敦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是任旧日本政府第二届枢木政权官房长官的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在战后亡命到了中华联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现认为他是乘着ZERO的活动所引起的内部局势不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而采取了这次行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在调查黑色骑士团是否参与了这次行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天的雷达基地爆炸…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们好像并不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包括Sakuradite开采权在内的事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是对方单方面主张的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  我们应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}九州战役
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泽崎的组织与九州地区内的恐怖组织协力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在破坏了连接本州与四国地区的陆上交通网之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在中华联邦辽东军管区的支援下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以福冈  长崎  奥羽为中心扩大占领范围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦的曹将军宣称这只不过是人道支援
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马尼拉会议与墨尔本议定书…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他说如果这是作战的话就服从
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  修耐泽尔殿下在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,东京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于朱雀的问题就这样定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说主君不在  这个问题一定要解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gefjun Disturber的对策还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有成为你的骑士的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是违反命令的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔哥哥说那是非常时期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要负上责任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原谅不了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成为你的负担了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我封你为骑士这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样地话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  杀了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却没有受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逍遥自在的活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又像这样被保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在殉职者和11区人的庇护下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我  没有这个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,资格这种东西  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,损伤太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种天气下也不能使用空路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上陆作战还是等天气安定下来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这风暴真是巧合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在应该可以平定九州
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曹将军  老天站在我们一边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争一定能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要发布戒严令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只会增加市民的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送我的亲笔信给EU的甘道鲁夫外相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有接通柬埔寨的特鲁默机关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特鲁默那边不太好控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宰相阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么我能帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为11区的副总督  我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了  有这份心意就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,『让副总督什么也别做』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是总督的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我擅自决定了骑士  也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是因为这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木的事我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就理解一下吧  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为是这种时候  科奈莉娅也没有多余的精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达尔顿  关于刚才的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识的人有渠道  我去拜托一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么努力地准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学园祭果然会被中止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那种问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要发生战争了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方要建立流亡政府
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是和中华联邦的战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜  预定要向美术馆借的室外摊位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去办手续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话在那之后要去一下科学部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于那个礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了罗伊德老师一下就说要给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个花心男
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  你给我继续工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是在做三人份的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的一个笨蛋玩人间蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修那家伙真是变了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还在混乱着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路竟然会是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有对任何人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要和鲁路见面  直接向他确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Z01 Float Touchment Contact
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,控制线路确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,悬浮模拟训练的结果是顶级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么辞去了骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是这样的我  由菲米娅皇女殿下也承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  如果给她添麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉她会变得自我厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓶副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这我一开始就明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还是想努力做到能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  克洛维斯哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我见到了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可没能替你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还想不出能拯救鲁路修和娜娜莉的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有像姐姐和修耐泽尔哥哥那样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了哪里都是拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等察觉时  发现都是自己在任性而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然违背了姐姐的意思选了骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但又被他拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  的确是听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只是书面手续就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有皇族的人正在观览
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问是哪一位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会和泽崎会合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那并不是独立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是傀儡政府
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们以日本为名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过改变了名字和主君而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样是没有未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种『日本』无视就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那样就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么放任布里塔尼亚的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  还是表明一下组织的明确目标的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泽崎的事先放在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的目标还是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京建立独立国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,独立？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,国家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我们  国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  果然你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在黑色骑士团壮大了  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人可是支配了世界三分之一以上的大国啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事只靠我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们准备等什么人来打倒布里塔尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人来代替自己做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等待的话总有一天机会会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己不行动起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天是永远不会来临的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs27}确认周围情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs27}状况δ发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs27}状况δ发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  我只是想向由菲米娅殿下道谢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一眼就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs27}封锁全部通路  重复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs27}封锁全部通往建筑的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭店那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好审讯室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻带走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话上陆作战就能重新展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔殿下的提案也应该能实行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为特派能够突破吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木的话有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他真是一个让人难以处置的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠技术力是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是从空中发射来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,距离被击中还有1分05秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害  反空袭对策做的真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我扫清弹幕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个方向过来的没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,命中确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌航空舰击破
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  就算是最新式的  只靠一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能为Lancelot证明实力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木少校  再度确认一遍作战概要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰以此高度突破敌方前线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在向敌方出发点移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向导兵器Z01-Lancelot使用Float Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对敌方司令部福冈基地进行强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  Float会急剧消耗能源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请留意启动时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ME Booster
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot  离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌舰上有轰炸机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是速度却在战斗机之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉影像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不是空运而是单独飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  是报告中的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个骑装兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[骑装兵器:中华联邦对KnightMare的称呼]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  驾驶舱里的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想占据九州地区的家伙的大义名分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为泽崎敦的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  没有他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新日本政府就会土崩瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦也就失去了介入的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是  敌人的司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公用频道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是泽崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向这边来的人是枢木的儿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  原来有这样的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候  由菲米娅大人救了我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀着光芒的女神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该感谢您借了我衣服才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  我其实不是那么出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐她们比起来  其实我实在是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果由菲米娅大人没用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样一点优点都没有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一点都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,双亲也是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点儿都不漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事  你非常可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的一点用也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算心里明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀的事也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊  朱雀也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  由菲米娅大人不要再说自己不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你见面太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和父亲没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了让战斗结束才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你投降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算夺走日本独立的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  应该用正确的手段来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想一直那样任性下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持你那种没有理念的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,VARIS被
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是中华联邦的钢髅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只用对话就能扰乱他的阵脚  还太嫩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修耐泽尔哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我私人通信的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能源包已经空了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  连Float都被破坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个Avalon直接向基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,防御壁不是全方位的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被击落的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  把能源只用在战斗与通讯上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证  会把你作为枢木首相的遗孤来礼遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在这里使用了父亲的名字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就无法原谅自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你还真是像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顽固的地方和你父亲真是相像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  这回怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  私事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换  我会变得很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  你顽固的地方  温柔的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伤感的眼神  笨拙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会被猫咬的地方  我全部都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  反而让你担心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇时也是  说自己是皇女的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,决定学校的时候也是  选我做骑士的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  总是突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我突然意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为这个出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉我心中的门被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么  赶快阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后拜托你一件事可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论我发生了什么  请你不要讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  请将我的一切都抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想给朋友惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉他们我转校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  难道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能源已经用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请代我向塞希尔、罗伊德和修耐泽尔殿下问好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后我都很自以为是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  别死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷达有了反应  是突然出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到了影像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个白壳是叫Lancelot吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是和以前一样乱来的战斗方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次好像作好了充分的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以单机来扰乱本阵  作为游击部队来使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使失败了  也能方便科奈莉娅的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个策略  是修耐泽尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强粒子炮不是应该还未完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能够收束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来应该由我来完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠Gefjun Disturber的技术理论总算是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是悬浮系统的开发是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然对手是布丁伯爵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意料之外的共同作业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木  Lancelot还能行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是公用频道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把声音放大  确认他的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能源包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要开始进攻敌方的司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愿望无法实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会抢在你之前进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全体出击  阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO和枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  你们不是为日本而战的同志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们黑色骑士团是所有使用不正当武力的人的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不正当？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是为了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泽崎  如果是为了日本的话为什么要逃到中华联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该为了保持尊严和大家一起留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,共同作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gawain和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀和鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  和枢木一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃过布里塔尼亚的耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而让Gawain单独行动看来是正确的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让红莲作护卫的话应该会更轻松些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我家和学校都回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在即使不和Lancelot联手也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所需要的不是胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是黑色骑士团在这场战役中曾参与过的这一事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然表面上的报道是不会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但暗地里也可以流出消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如ZERO所言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些将会对把我们的立场传达给世界起重要的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向外国寻求援助等待时机有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这才应该是所谓的战略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,龟岛还留有防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泽崎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九州最大的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然如此简单就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九州地区所爆发的反体制恐怖主义事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在科奈莉娅总督所指挥的闪电作战下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕了泽崎敦  及其下四名旧日本政府的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏了半数以上参与行动的中华联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦首脑部宣称这次的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是辽东军管区曹将军的独断行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并要求按西藏条约进行俘虏交换
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀  现在正式返回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和理想的国家  大义这种复杂的东西无关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想看到笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在最喜欢的人和曾经最喜欢的人的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮助我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经击毁了泽崎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不得不迅速实行下一步行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最优先构筑娜娜莉生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个  要建造能够约束世界的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏后的构筑正顺利地进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就把科奈莉娅和修耐泽尔  两人一起…
